The thumbnail repaints itself only if a source figure is repainted. 
So if the thumbnail is not a child of the source figure, it is not 
infinitely repainted over and over. See a method Thumbnail.notifyPainting(). 
Great. I hope it works. I guess that's why we went through the trouble of 
passing around the Map of dirty regions.
